OL,5, A British family taken in by a local   
OL,6, family when their hotel in Rhodes was  
OL,7, evacuated say it has "restored their   
OL,8, faith in human kindness".              
OL,10,FCaryn Savazzi from South Wales arrived 
OL,11,Fon the island with her husband and sons
OL,12,Fon Saturday, unaware their hotel had   
OL,13,Falready been evacuated amid wildfires. 
OL,15,FThey were taken to a school, where a   
OL,16,Flocal family offered them shelter.     
OL,18,FBut other Britons remain without a bed.
